  "content": "ght: 700; margin-bottom: 8px;\">Grid Collapse</h3>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.5;\">\n          4-column grid collapses to one. Side by side becomes stacked.\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"card\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-blue); padding: 24px 32px;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size: 26px; line-height: 1.5;\">\n      <strong>The frustrating part:</strong> fix one issue, ask for another change,\n      and a <em>different</em> alignment breaks.\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"stat-grid\" style=\"grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; margin-top: 8px;\">\n    <div class=\"stat-box\" style=\"padding: 20px;\">\n      <div class=\"stat-value\" style=\"font-size: 48px; color: var(--accent-red);\">~3&ndash;5x</div>\n      <div class=\"stat-label\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\">More iterations (est.)</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"stat-box\" style=\"padding: 20px;\">\n      <div class=\"stat-value\" style=\"font-size: 48px; color: var(--accent-amber);\">Most</div>\n      <div class=\"stat-label\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Fixes broke more</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"stat-box\" style=\"padding: 20px;\">\n      <div class=\"stat-value\" style=\"font-size: 48px; color: var(--accent-purple);\">0</div>\n      <div class=\"stat-label\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Visual errors self-caught</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"flex-grow\"></div>\n  <div class=\"author-tag\">Lim Chun Zhe</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-number\">04 / 08</div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->\n<!-- SLIDE 5: WHY THIS HAPPENS                       -->\n<!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->\n<div class=\"slide\">\n  <div class=\"slide-label\">The Root Cause</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-title\">\n    A Designer Who<br>\n    <span class=\"highlight-purple\">Can't Look Up</span><br>\n    From the Code\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"slide-subtitle\">\n    The gap isn't intelligence. It's perception.\n  </div>",
